[ROLE declarer][STAGE post-play] West's diamond length — revealed as the suit unwound — placed the queen on the left, so the ten finesse toward dummy was the winning direction. Vacant places did the work: count the side suits, find the long hand, and play it for the queen of trumps-or-diamonds. Ten tricks, well counted.}
